message:
Thankful for those that go the extra step. 
"The first inclination of any officer who never worked a trafficking case would be, ‘OK, thanks for your time, ma’am.’ Instead, Ryan sat down, and heard her out.”

data.description: Ryan Baillie, of the Martinez police department, reflects on how he connected the dots in a huge human trafficking case.
data.title: How a small-town detective solved one of the Bay Area’s biggest human trafficking cases
